{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"455a11031b","title":"致陈毅、宋时轮等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c88e036ed9","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":11,"articleId":"455a11031b"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"790b883dca","type":"paragraph","text":"致陈毅、宋时轮等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"455a11031b"},{"id":"bcf69a851e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年9月11日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"455a11031b"},{"id":"48860fe560","type":"paragraph","text":"故六个旅南下，两淮危急回，票率苏中主力（一、六师）立即开两淮，准各配合陈宋主力彻底开灭该敌。但陈、宋现应独立作战，务于票、谭到达前歼灭南下之敌一个至两个旅，顿挑敌之前进，争取时间，以待苏中主力到达，协力轩敌全部。[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致陈毅、宋时轮、张鼎丞、邓子恢、栗裕、谭震林电的主要内容。12]8月上旬，山东野战军进攻酒县失利后，撤至泗阳休整。9月10日起国民党军沿运河两岸南下，进犯两淮","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"455a11031b"}],"page":{"id":"85639d9f37","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"455a11031b","start":155,"end":155}}}},"__N_SSG":true}